com.bergerkiller.reflection.net.minecraft.server

Class NMSVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.reflection.net.minecraft.server.NMSVector

  • public class NMSVector
extends java.lang.Object
    All NMS Vector related classes can be used here. Vec3D, ChunkCoordIntPair and BlockPosition are supported. No reflection is used to minimize overhead.
